data.description: Great Deal and Priced to Sell. Very Spacious 3 bedroom 2 Bath double wide mobile home on over 1.25 Acres of land.  This home is settled in the Viking area with so much potential. Come in to the Very open split floor plan which features beautiful vinyl flooring throughout and a Large Gorgeous Fireplace. The Kitchen features a eat in Island and plenty of cabinets and counter space. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this hidden gem with so much privacy and land.  Roof was replaced last year with a metal roof. The air conditioning is not working, it will either need to be repaired or replaced. Priced for a Quick Sale.
